riod after placing a 20% deposit to reserve)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Completion Dec. 2026 </span></p>',1,'',1751439509,1758272991),(44,'RIARA OASIS','RIARA OASIS','RIARA OASIS','RIARA OASIS',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/4e331284efc327448d46378ec1f0a71bead96233.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/ee9266219e78a6a09c29776e32b0f7abcc55a465.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/12cbc556fce6afc68eebdbf625ed49f13b3dad10.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/12cbc556fce6afc68eebdbf625ed49f13b3dad10.jpeg','','','','36.767876416','-1.296009067',52995,145494,145535,'Riara road','Riara road','1',1751439600,100000.00,5000000.00,15000000.00,'2',1,1,1,0,25,0,142.00,50.00,'<p><br></p>','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>RIARA OASIS</strong></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Riara Oasis, a landmark residential development located along the tranquil and leafy </span><a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/A4UUWoAvzqMw2h9y5\" target=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Riara Road</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> in Lavington, Nairobi. Spanning 0.83 acres, this visionary project features three magnificent 22-floor towers offering a curated collection of 1, 2, and 3-bedroom modern apartments for sale, all crafted for sophisticated urban living.</span></p><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Lifestyle Amenities That Elevate Everyday Living:</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Riara Oasis is fully equipped to deliver comfort, convenience, and community through a suite of top-tier amenities:</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Fully Equipped Gym</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Children’s Play Area</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Swimming Pool</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Borehole Water Supply &amp; Water Purifier</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">4-Level Ample Parking</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">CCTV Surveillance &amp; Visual Conversational Systems</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">High-Speed Lifts</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Integrated Security Systems with Professional Guards</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1 Bedroom Units</span></div><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Sizes: 50m² – 68m</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Types: 6 unique layouts</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Price Range: From KSh 5.5M to KSh 7M</span></li></ul><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 Bedroom Units</span></div><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Sizes: 88m² – 95m²</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Types: 2 configurations</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Price Range: From KSh 9.5M to KSh 10M</span></li></ul><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3 Bedroom Units</span></div><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Sizes: 120m² – 135m²</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Types: 3 expansive designs</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Price Range: From KSh 13.5M to KSh 15M</span></li></ul><h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Prime Location in Lavington:</span></h2><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Riara Oasis is located in the prestigious Lavington suburb, offering excellent connectivity to:</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Top international schools</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Shopping malls (The Junction, Yaya Centre)</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Hospitals, restaurants, and entertainment hubs</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Quick access to Ngong Road, Gitanga Road &amp; Nairobi CBD</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Expected Completion</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">: December 2027<br></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Flexible Payment Plans:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">20%, 30%, or 50% deposit</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Balance payable in easy installments up to December 2027</span></li></ul>',1,'',1751441136,1758010224),(46,'JADE RESIDENCE','JADE RESIDENCE','JADE RESIDENCE','JADE RESIDENCE',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/b47df5a39ab4ac2e2eebe5c19351b5237998a322.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/5dca79cc8e09089cfe4736680073fcb918d7724a.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/ff6ec9c4b8baf7680f86e03dd3af046ee3ef8137.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/4a284e759deaf820593acc65cb5250fc451b0a17.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/d3d5e040ad9f92654e65859e492ebbf0835163df.jpg','','','','115.9243610','28.6347270',52995,145494,145535,'Kindaruma road,Kilimani','Kindaruma road,Kilimani','0',1751353200,121495.00,13000000.00,4300000.00,'1',1,1,1,0,25,1,310.00,107.00,'<p><br></p>','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>JADE RESIDENCY</strong></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The Jade Residency offers luxury living within the city. Offering luxury apartments that are centrally located in Kilimani area in Nairobi. Close proximity to major shopping malls, schools. Hospitals and other amenities, all within a 2 km radius. The boutique development comprising 2, 3 and 4 bed luxury apartments has been tastefully designed with world class finishes. 114 units in total</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Amenities:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Provision for gym space</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Roof top gym facility, </span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Roof top social hall with kitchenette</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Roof top open terrace lounge</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Sky bridge connecting both blocks</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">High speed lifts,</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Dedicated parking spots,</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Generator for common areas</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Provision for intercom, internet and satellite TV,</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Private balconies</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Provision for an inverter in each apartment, </span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微