isure Space</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ?‍♀️ Heated Swimming Pool</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ? Office Space and Conference Room</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ⁠? Convenience Store</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ☕️ Coffee Bar</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ? 24-hour Security &amp; CCTV</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ? Borehole Water with Purifier</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">– ⚡️ Full Backup Generator</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\">1 Bedroom 78 sqm Ksh 8.5M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">1 Bedroom 90 sqm Ksh 9.5 M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">2 Bedroom 96 &nbsp;sqm Ksh 10.5M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">2 Bedroom + Dsq 166 sqm Ksh 15.5M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">3 Bedroom 180 sqm Ksh 19 M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">3 &nbsp;Bedroom+ Study + Dsq 208 sqm 21.5 M</li><li style=\"text-align: left;\">3 Bedroom + 