tta International Airport, the location ensures seamless access to key city landmarks.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Key Features of the Development</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Spacious Lounge</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Large Windows for Natural Lighting</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Extended Balcony in the Living Area</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Semi-Open Kitchen with Premium Granite Worktops</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Separate Laundry Area with Balcony for Drying Clothes</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Elevated Dual Bar in the Semi-Open Kitchen</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">Apartment Finishes &amp; Details</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">​</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Imported Granite Tiles in Hall and Kitchen</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Glazed Ceramic Tiles in Bathrooms &amp; Utility Areas</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Textured Acrylic Paint for External Finishing</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">• Internal Walls Painted to High Standards</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"