,'0',1783580400,203869.00,15700000.00,93000000.00,'14',100,1,1,0,27,1,623.00,77.00,'<p><br></p><p><u><strong>3-BEDROOM HOUSE FOR SALE RIVERSIDE, NAIROBI FROM 12.8M TO &nbsp;93.2M</strong></u></p><p>Discover comfort and convenience in this beautifully maintained <strong>3-bedroom house located in the heart of RIVERSIDE NAIROBI</strong>, one of Nairobi’s most sought-after residential neighborhoods. Ideal for families, professionals, or investors, this property offers a perfect blend of privacy, space, and easy access to essential amenities.</p><p><strong>�� Property Features and Amenities:</strong></p><p>· 3 spacious bedrooms, including a master ensuite</p><p>· Bright and airy living and dining area</p><p>· Modern kitchen with ample storage</p><p>· Well-maintained bathrooms with quality fittings</p><p>· Private garden and outdoor sitting space</p><p>· Secure parking for 2+ vehicles</p><p>· Reliable water supply and backup systems</p><p>· Gated compound with 24-hour security</p><p><strong>�� Prime Location in RIVERSIDE NAIROBI:</strong></p><p>Situated in a serene and secure environment, this home is just minutes away from key facilities:</p><p>· �� <strong>Top Schools:</strong><br>Nearby institutions include CONSOLATA ACADEMY School, NAIROBI UNIVERSITY, and MORE SCHOOLS.</p><p>· </p><p>· �� <strong>Shopping & Dining:</strong><br>Moments away from CLOSE TO BOTH NAIROBI WESTLANDS YAYA AND LAVINGTON SHOPPING CENTRE, offering a variety of restaurants, cafes, supermarkets, and shops.</p><p>· �� <strong>Excellent Road Access:</strong><br>Just a short drive to the <strong>Nairobi Expressway</strong>, providing quick connectivity to Westlands, CBD, JKIA, and beyond.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Unit Size and Unit Price</strong></p><p>1 bedroom, 77 -110 sqm KSH.12,800,000.</p><p>2 bedroom, 132sqm-185 SQM &nbsp;KSH. 21.4M.</p><p>3 bedroom, 218-285 SQM KSH. 38,000,000.</p><p>4 BEDROOM DUPLEX &nbsp;623-900SQM &nbsp;93.2M</p><p> </p><p><strong>Payment Plan</strong></p><p>20% downpayment &nbsp;RANGE MAY VARY.</p><p>Balance spread until completion(range may vary).</p><p> </p><p><strong>Completion Date</strong></p><p>0711726777</p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>THE SARUNI RESIDENCE</strong></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The Saruni, is a unique contemporary development that is the embodiment of a luxurious lifestyle secluded from the hustle and bustle of the fast-paced urban life.The development provides a luxurious refuge away from the high paced energy of city life with an extensive list of amenities specifically curated for an environment of leisure, serenity and rejuvenation. With uninterrupted views from each apartment.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The Saruni , is a modern interpretation of contemporary luxury specifically designed to enhance your living experience.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">It consists of a total of 18 floors, with 95 units, 131 parking slots and 13 visitors parking slots.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Property Features and Amenities:</strong></span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">East and West Sky Gardens</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Infinity heated swimming pool</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Steam room</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Modern fitted gym</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Reception lobby and management office</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 High speed lifts</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Ground level manicured and landscaped</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">courtyard garden</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Ample parking</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Full backup generator</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">24 Hr security services at the gate and on property</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Intercom</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Perimeter electric fence</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-ali