: start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">b) Other Payments:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">If a buyer wishes to make upfront payments, a discounted price may be considered.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Estimated completion date; December 2024</span></p>',1,'',1751534614,1758197931),(88,'ROYAL LEGEND','ROYAL LEGEND','ROYAL LEGEND','ROYAL LEGEND',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250703/fe4c4c84f7e2719861a123781c0341297c71b5e5.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/3b22fcc9104e7e868b8302a6dce7bf7e87afadab.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/87c717562ded497591d8f0d4f1d989b765338061.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/06e75c85460fb16077f1ed7bd954bf87c4e5596f.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/2ed7a89d5b85022a4c4aec41d25aefc37efd3ee0.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250916/7f83fe8f4e89f191c15a5dff5d269f34b24cb177.jpeg','','','','117.5728200','29.5294750',52995,145494,145535,'Ndemi road','Ndemi road','1',1783407600,125000.00,12000000.00,62500000.00,'5',4,1,1,0,25,1,446.00,96.00,'<ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"></li></ul>','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>ROYAL LEGEND RESIDENCE</strong></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Royal Legend Residence is the world of opulence and sophistication where every detail has been meticulously crafted to offer you an unmatched living experience in the heart of Lavington. We are thrilled to introduce you to a range of modern, high-end apartments that cater to all your needs, from cozy two-bedroom units to expansive five-bedroom homes, perfect for families or roommates. Whatever your lifestyle, we have the ideal apartment for you.</span></