cess to shopping malls, international schools, and key business hubs.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Modern Design &amp; Spacious Units: Choose from various apartment layouts ranging from 60m² to 150m², all featuring elegant interiors, high-end finishes, and contemporary designs.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Flexible Payment Plan: Secure your dream home today with just a 20% deposit and spread the balance in convenient installments until December 2025.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Premium Apartment Features:</span></h3><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Each unit is fitted with:</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Modern Kitchen: This kitchen comes with 2 fitted burners, an exhaust fan, and a light belt for added convenience.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Elegant Lighting – Beautiful chandeliers to elevate your living space.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Extra Storage – The 3-bedroom units include a spacious pantry.</span></li></ul><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> Apartment Prices &amp; Sizes:</span></h3><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1-Bedroom Apartments (5 types) – 60m² to 70m² | KES 7.6M – 8.8M</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2-Be