">Verde Vista in Lavington is a residential development offering five bespoke villas, each situated on a one-acre plot, designed with a focus on nature and privacy. These homes feature 5 ensuite bedrooms, a private lift, and spacious garden areas. They are designed with a nature-focused approach, preserving mature trees on-site and incorporating elements of greenery throughout the development. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>FEATURES:</strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Spacious Villas:Each villa boasts 5 ensuite bedrooms spread across approximately 6,500 sq ft, spread over three levels.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Nature-Focused Design:The development emphasizes the preservation of existing mature trees and incorporates abundant greenery.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Privacy and Exclusivity:The development consists of only five villas, ensuring a sense of privacy and tranquility.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Modern Amenities:Features include a private lift in each home, a top-floor entertainment lounge with panoramic views, and 4-car parking with additional visitor spaces.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Quiet and Secure Location:, Located in a quiet and safe area on Jacaranda Avenue, known for its beautiful landscaping.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Community and Convenience:</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Close to international schools, shopping malls, and other amenities.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Location:</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Verde Vista is situated on Jacaranda Avenue, a tree-lined street in Lavington</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Verde Vista is marketed towards families, entertainers, and those seeking refined tranquility. The development aims to provide a peaceful and nature-rich living environment while still offering convenient access to urban amenities. </span></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">5 Bedroom 145 sqm 22,000,000</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p>',1,'',1751629483,1758191338),(103,'FINSBURY HEIGHTS','FINSBURY HEIGHTS','FINSBURY HEIGHTS','FINSBURY HEIGHTS',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250704/0505170b7dbb894a6eceb5957a06ec923463c891.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250704/87025bfd952f0b39d1524a6701ee9067b842fc3a.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250704/5763eaf3aae1038fd363374912d2ff664e08442d.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eS_sDKKXwYM&pp=ygUQRmluc2J1cnkgSGVpZ2h0cw%3D%3D','https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250704/a4c378bab12ab051ad08102c6071335057d8cbde.jpg','','128.5164702','40.5627219',52995,145494,145534,'Crescent rd, Westlands, Nairobi','Crescent rd, Westlands, Nairobi','1',1801515600,96750.00,11610000.00,19350000.00,'46',24,1,1,1,27,1,255.00,120.00,'<p>Finsbury Heights is a residential development in Nairobi, Kenya, offering spacious 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments with luxurious amenities. It\'s located off Parklands Road in Westlands, near the border with Parklands. Finsbury Heights is known for its blend of modern living, convenience, and community atmosphere.</p><ul><li>Key features of Finsbury Heights:</li><li>Location:Prime location in Nairobi, specifically in the Westlands area, situated between Parklands and Westlands.</li><li>Apartment types:Offers a range of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments, including some with servant\'s quarters (DSQ).</li><li>Amenities:Includes a rooftop pool, mosque, gym, children\'s play area, on-site supermarket, and ample parking.</li><li>Security:Features 24/7 CCTV and manned security, ensuring a safe living environment, according to Instagram posts by UrbanGlow Real Estate.</li><li>Modern living:Highlights fully fitted kitchens, and a sustainable borehole for water supply.</li><li>Community:Promotes a vibrant community atmosphere</li></ul>','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><u><strong>FINSBURY HEIGHTS</strong></u></span></p><p>Finsbury Heights is a residential development in Nairobi, Kenya, offering spacious 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments with luxurious amenities. It\'s located off Parklands Road in Westlands, near the border with Parklands. Finsbury Heights is known for its blend of modern living, convenience, and community atmosphere. </p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Key features of Finsbury Heights:</strong></span></p><ul><li>Location:Prime location in Nairobi, specifically in the Westlands area, situated between Parklands and Westlands.</li><li>Apartment types:Offers a range of 2, 3, and 4-bedroom apartments, including some with servant\'s quarters (DSQ).</li><li>Amenities:Includes a rooftop pool, mosque, gym, children\'s play area, on-site supermarket, and ample parking.</li><li>Security:Features 24/7 CCTV and manned security, ensuring a safe living environment, accor &nbsp;ding to Instagram posts by UrbanGlow Real Estate.</li><li>Modern living:Highlights fully fitted kitchens, and a sustainable borehole for water supply.</li><li>Community:Promotes a vibrant community atmosphere</li></ul>',1,'',1751630178,1756461805),(104,'STANDALONE HOUSE','STANDALONE HOUSE','STANDALONE HOUSE','STANDALONE HOUSE',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250812/79b9369fb87673a8d499ca4b95336d22d63889e2.jpeg','','','','115.3613413','26.3246275',52995,145494,145534,'Loresho','Loresho','4',1751353200,136709.00,108000000.00,108000000.00,'11',11,1,2,0,26,1,790.00,790.00,'<p><br></p>','<p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0,