top Restaurant</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Landscaped Zen Garden</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Borehole Water Supply</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Full Backup Generator</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">High-Speed Lifts</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">CCTV &amp; Biometric Security</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> &nbsp;Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Furnished Studio</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> (45sqm): From KSh 6.6M</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>One Bedroom</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> (64sqm): From KSh 7.85M</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Two Bedroom</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> (97-130sqm): From KSh 10.95M</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Payment plan:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">10% deposit balance within 3 years with 0% Interest. </span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Completion date:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Project estimated completion December 2027</span></li></ul>',1,'',1752499516,1757682436),(157,'KINGS COURTYARD','KINGS COURTYARD','KINGS COURTYARD','KINGS COURTYARD',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/caedc2f6a3bd67becf1155b659b5f2c83ab68a42.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/f1483e2197ad9ca2f392d3f163871f17ea211aba.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/0b833aacbd4b39de3ad6ecaec3750d33196a2240.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/2a34ed32cd19a49b00c5aaa02bbd743480412e50.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/a8efa74dc3cd7d4183f0b1311630495324baf821.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250714/3e3b0b3e5d8fa78c6db5a83b1806ad22f7c87d94.jpg','','https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/a8efa74dc3cd7d4183f0b1311630495324baf821.jpg','','36.795651245','-1.288830475',52995,145494,145535,'Kilimani, Lenana rd.','Kilimani, Lenana rd.','1',1752476400,119631.00,13000000.00,19500000.00,'0',0,1,1,0,30,1,163.00,111.00,'<p><br></p>','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>KINGS COURTYARD</strong></u></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Situated along Lenana Road in the Kilimani neighbourhood of Westlands Sub‑county, about 5 km west of Nairobi’s CBD &nbsp;.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Easily accessible — just 5 minutes from Kilimani Police Station, 10 minutes to the city centre, and 8 minutes from Nairobi Arboretum &nbsp;.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Close to Yaya Centre, cafés, schools, hospitals, embassies, and banks &nbsp;.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Amenities &amp; Features:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Kings Courtyard offers a host of upscale features geared toward comfortable and modern urban living:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Recreational &amp; Community Facilities: Rooftop leisure pool, fitness &amp; recreation centre, children’s play area, community hall &nbsp;.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Security &amp; Access: Secured boundary walls, controlled entry/exit with automatic barriers, CCTV coverage of key areas, high‑speed elevators in each block &nbsp;.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Utilities: Backup generator for common areas, solar lighting in shared spaces, borehole water supply, inverter backup capability, anti‑termite foundation, cabro‑paved driveways &nbsp;.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Apartment Interiors: All bedrooms ensuite, branded bathroom fittings, designer sanitary ware, provision for gas cylinder in kitchen yard, TV points, fibre/Wi‑Fi readiness, balconies offering views &nbsp;.</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> Unit Types &amp; Pricing:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Unit Type Size Price (KES)</span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 Bedroom (all ensuite) ~102 m² (1,100 ft²) ~13.5M (SOLD OUT) &nbsp;</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3 Bedroom (all ensuite) ~162 – 163 m² (1,750 ft²) From ~18.5–19.5M </span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 bed units priced around KES 13.5M — quickly sold out.</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3 bed units start around KES 19.5M, with some listings showing KES 18M (depending on size and timing) &nbsp;.</span></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Completion date:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Developed by Kings Developers Limited, this is a deluxe‑grade residential tower expected for completion between Q3 2025 and December 2027 &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">.</span></p>',1,'',1752500903,1760360566),(158,'MONTEBLUE','MONTEBLUE','MONTEBLUE','MONTEBLUE',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250715/9fd2c48702750b3c4a60235f423ad79bcb5458ed.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250715/43315065c99eb5423c3a14da8541a180739484ec.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250715/0a9941e781704035a56ead2706a52e6882ea88ce.jpeg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250715/ec6fee6f86137a577c3575cdaad5e08ee44a7204.jpeg','','','','36.812748447','-1.265077126',52995,145494,145534,'Muthithi road,Westlands','Muthithi road,Westlands','1',1817449200,112500.00,6750000.00,12950000.00,'34',34,1,1,0,25,1,116.00,60.00,'<p><br></p>','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>MONTEBLUE APARTMENTS</strong></u></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Montbleu Apartments offer luxury 1 &amp; 2 bedroom residences in the heart of Westlands, blending modern elegance with hotel-style amenities. Ideal for both living and investment, these stylish apartments feature a rooftop pool, gym, clubhouse, and more. Prices start from KSh 6.75M for 1-bedroom units and KSh 11.85M for 2-bedroom units. With flexible payment plans and a construction timeline from November 2024 to November 2027, Montbleu is your perfect urban retreat.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Unit Details &amp; Pricing:</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>1 Bedroom Apartments</strong></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   Standard: 60 sqm – From KSh 6.75M\n•   Premium: 61 sqm – KSh 6.95M</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>2 Bedroom Apartments</strong></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   Standard: 104 sqm – KSh 11.85M\n•   Premium: 116 sqm – From KSh 12.95M</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Hotel-Style Amenities</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">:</span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   Rooftop Swimming Pool\n•   Social Clubhouse\n•   Rooftop Fully Fitted Gym\n•   Reception Lobby\n•   Sky Lounge\n•   Conference Room\n•   Children’s Play Area\n•   Spa &amp; Salon Space\n•   Restaurant Cafe\n•   Mini Mart\n•   Four High-Speed Lifts\n•   Fully Backup Generator</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Security &amp; Convenience</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">:</span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   CCTV Surveillance\n•   Electric Fence\n•   Internet Connectivity\n•   Borehole Water Supply\n•   Ample Parking\n•   Solar Water-Heating System</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Payment Plans:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Cash Installment Buyer</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">:</span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   10% booking fee\n•   10% upon signing of sales agreement\n•   75% over construction period\n•   5% on completion</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Mortgage Buyer:</strong></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   10% booking fee\n•   20% upon signing of sales agreement\n•   70% on completion through mortgage</code></pre><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Construction Timeline:</strong></span></p><pre style=\"text-align: left;\"><code>•   Start: November 2024\n•   Completion: November 2027 (36 months)</code></pre><p><br></p>',1,'',1752563161,1757682496),(159,'KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE','KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE','KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE','KITISURU FALLS RESDENCE',4,'blob:https://www.afbeke.com/b259bb54-6e14-4733-8992-6ffb2129408f,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250918/e043f43433de71cdb43eedc1500f5d9ba27dd9fd.jpg,blob:https://www.afbeke.com/3655c139-ffc0-4bbf-bf39-d6ce7f90127a','','','','36.799864769','-1.216558587',52995,145494,145564,'Kitisuru','Kitisuru','1',1752562800,118182.00,6500000.00,12000000.00,'16',16,1,1,0,26,1,120.00,55.00,'<p><br></p>','<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>KITISURU FALLS RESIDENCE</strong></u></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Nestled just minutes from the landmark Kitisuru Falls Residence, our newest address THE KITISURU GROVE offers a refreshed sense of serenity and seclusion in one of Nairobi’s most coveted suburbs.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Surrounded by verdant landscapes and mature trees, this intimate collection of modern homes blends the best of nature and urban convenience. With Westlands, Village Market, the CBD, and JKIA all within a 30-minute radius, this project is designed for those who crave a quiet retreat without leaving the pulse of the city behind.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Here, you’re not buying just an apartment—you’re investing in mornings filled with birdsong, evening strolls under the canopy of indigenous trees, and a community shaped by calm, convenience, and class.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">This is the next chapter in the Kitisuru story. A natural evolution from the falls to the grove, from the view to the vibe.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The location enjoys good infrastructure, such as the Redhill Link Road connecting to Westlands and the &nbsp;Express Way- which connects to JKIA and Mombasa Road. Other nearby road connections are the New Western Bypass, Southern Bypass, and the Great North Road, which all connect the area with other towns and counties.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> Key Features:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Spacious Kitchen.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Cozy Living Room.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Spacious and accommodating Living Room</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Magnificent Lighting Features.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Access to public transportation.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The apartment is secured with boundary perimeter wall, street lighting and 24/7 security among other features.</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> Amenities:</strong></span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Minutes &nbsp;away from Muthaiga Golf Club, Tribe Hotel in Village Market among other social amenities.</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">We have Churches, Mosques and Temples in the Neighborhood .</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Accessible to the JKIA Airport through Red Hill Link road which connects to the new express highway</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">12Kms from Nairobi CBD</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">15 Mins drive from Sarit Centre Westland, Westgate, Village Market, UNEP Headquarters Gigiri &amp; US Embassy</span></div><p><br></p><p><br></p>',1,'',1752565033,1758186806),(160,'','PANORAMA WEST','','NWC',4,'https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250918/80bd1c7307cdd1e7523c0c6282fe17fae07f3623.jpg,blob:https://www.afbeke.com/7b1d6e81-751c-4192-bcd7-cebae8dc8579,blob:https://www.afbeke.com/b3e6dfdb-4e2c-47f2-b51e-2e932fe649f5,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250918/817842bc97f33dbfc2a037581d55145290718059.jpg,blob:https://www.afbeke.com/6de2c9fd-6b45-4472-a55a-c45316c0f710','','','','36.769860600','-1.237565493',52995,145494,145534,'Westlands','Westlands','1',1819868400,132013.00,9200000.00,14770000.00,'17',20,1,1,0,27,1,111.00,69.69,'<p><br></p>','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>PANORAMA WEST RESIDENCE</strong></u></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Discover a sophisticated living experience with </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Panorama West Residence</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">, located on Mahiga Mairu Avenue, directly opposite Safaricom House in the heart of Westlands. Offering contemporary 1 and 2-bedroom apartments, this stunning development is perfect for both investors and homeowners seeking prime real estate.</span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> Premium Amenities:</strong></span></h3><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> &nbsp;Enjoy a range of top-tier amenities designed to enhance your lifestyle:</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Fully Equipped Gym</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Stay fit with cutting-edge workout equipment.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Children’s Playground</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – A safe and fun area for kids to play.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Heated Swimming Pool</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Relax and unwind in the temperature-controlled pool.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Recreation Club</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Socialize and entertain in style.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Yoga Room</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Find your zen in a peaceful, dedicated space.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Reading Lounge</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – A quiet spot to relax and enjoy your favorite book.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Coffee Bar</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Grab a coffee and socialize with neighbors.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>24-hour Security &amp; CCTV</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> – Round-the-clock security for your peace of mind.</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Borehole W