edroom and 3‑bedroom apartments, each with DSQ (domestic staff quarters) &nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Discover refined living in this spacious 4-bedroom villa boasting 212 sqm of thoughtfully designed space. Nestled within an exclusive gated community of just 15 units, this home offers privacy, security, and a welcoming neighborhood atmosphere.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The villa features:</strong></span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Master ensuite bedroom with a private balcony</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Two balconies for fresh air and relaxation</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Self-contained servant quarter (DSQ) for added convenience</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Personal parking accommodating up to 3 cars</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Small private garden perfect for outdoor leisure</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Bright, airy interiors designed for modern family living</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">This home blends comfort, elegance, and functionality — ideal for families seeking a peaceful yet connected lifestyle.</span></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">?</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; fon