t-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Sitting on 1 acre of land, these new 2 and 3-bedroom apartments for sale are strategically situated providing both investors and residents with outstanding value, offering high rental yields and a full residential experience.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Impala Heights is Thindigua’s urban jungle having set aside over 1,000 SQM of green space redefining modern residential living. These investment-turn key apartments will provide investors with a unique and excellent return on their investment changing the landscape of Thindigua’s Real Estate Market.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Thindigua’s location on Kiambu Road ensures that Impala Heights is not just a home, but a well-connected hub for both work and leisure.</span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">High Return on Investment</span></h3><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Thindigua, a rapidly developing satellite town, has become increasingly popular among tenants due its easy access to major cities and key roads like CBD, Westlands, Parklands, Upperhill and Limuru Road- which happen to be major employment &amp; commercial centers.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">This satellite town also houses and is in close proximity to major social amenities like schools, hospitals, banks making it possible for residents to enjoy the convenience of urban living in a peaceful, serene environment. For investors, all this factors assures you of consistent rental income and short-term capital growth making Impala Heights a profitable property to invest in.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">These apartments promise a high rental yield with an ROI of up to 8%, a projected capital growth of over 16% within 2 years and a flexible payment plan for over 2years.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Additionally, Thindigua is rapidly developing with an annual rental price increase of over 7%, making Impala Heights Apartments an attractive investment for both seasoned and first-time investors.</span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Family Living Redefined</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Designed with families in mind, Impala Heights offers spacious 2 and 3-bedroom apartments that cater to modern family needs. The well-thought-out layouts feature large rooms, ample natural light and, open-plan living spaces that foster connection and comfort.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">With amenities such as a heated swimming pool, gym, gaming room and kid’s play area, residents will enjoy a healthy and convenient lifestyle without leaving the premises.</span></p><h3><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Open Spaces &amp; Greenery for Enhanced Living</span></h3><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The design of Impala Heights incorporates extensive open spaces that will ensure a consistent flow of natural light and ventilation and, a spacious balcony that will make it possible for residents to enjoy fresh air and ample sunlight throughout the day.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The zen gardens and green spaces add tranquility, offering a peaceful retreat to relax, meditate, and connect with nature.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">These elements enhance the aesthetic appeal and overall living experience, making Impala Heights Apartments, a truly unique residential environment.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 Bedroom 102 sqm Ksh 9,000,000</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">3 Bedroom &nbsp;136 sqm Ksh 12,000,000</span></p>',1,'',1752738825,1758180105),(175,'SYOKIMAU VILLAS','SYOKIMAU VILLAS','SYOKIMAU VILLAS','SYOKIMAU VILLAS',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250717/2bb71810f483b4ab0516412cd912df8ff3066052.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250717/ef2231fddd5c629fe3f2a19df95f03fd124543be.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250717/679a24ca01f4bd3f9b5b5dad96eb8e899c1c5341.jpg','','https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250717/22fc404b6e6802b95065fd53fb5b864ae45a0813.jpg','','36.950798035','-1.364922151',52995,145494,145548,'Katani Rd, Syokimau','Katani Rd, Syokimau','1',1752735600,80189.00,16950000.00,17000000.00,'0',0,1,1,0,30,0,212.00,200.00,'<p><br></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><u><strong>SYOKIMAU VILLA</strong></u></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Discover refined living in this spacious 4-bedroom villa boasting 212 sqm of thoughtfully designed space. Nestled within an exclusive gated community of just 15 units, this home offers privacy, security, and a welcoming neighborhood atmosphere.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>The villa features:</strong></span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Master ensuite bedroom with a private balcony</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Two balconies for fresh air and relaxation</span></div><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"ch