todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked> A semi-open fitted kitchen equipped with modern conveniences. </div><p> <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Additionally,</strong></span></p><ul><li> There is a detached two-bedroom DSQ that shares utilities, providing convenience for household support. A guest cloakroom and an en-suite guest bedroom.</li><li><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Moving to the upper level:</strong></span></li></ul><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled checked>The master bedroom is a true retreat with its own balcony, bathtub, and shower cubicle. The three bedrooms on this level are all en-suite.<br><strong>One of the standout features of this property is the private swimming pool, providing a refreshing oasis for </strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><strong>relaxation and recreation.</strong></span></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Unit size and prize:</strong></span></p><p>5 Bedroom 700 sqm at Ksh 110,000,000</p><p><br></p>',1,'',1753775191,1756460985),(230,'OAK WEST RESIDENCY','OAK WEST RESIDENCY','OAK WEST RESIDENCY','OAK WEST RESIDENCY',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250702/edecfc821c5a0965c9f27eccb7583c8fae45a978.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250905/e59a3a53b5bc86bf2d1f53eeec0db4accdb47f73.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250905/aaf324a1fb48a113ccacd7d66ab40c792f3a1f23.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com/storage/default/20250905/3958920e03c9a9575f96dcb7868a88ce46e9b073.jpg','https://commercialpropertykenya.com/properties/oak-west-residency-in-westlands-nairobi/?srsltid=AfmBOoo4OpCXl7P_FrGshIX_Toen1LEsX96uWsipM0eUy26shwt5nNh6','','','35.956183346','-0.020164985',52995,145494,145534,'Mogotio road','Mogotio road','1',1825833600,139655.00,8100000.00,20000000.00,'12',100,1,1,0,27,1,150.00,58.00,'<p><br></p>','<h1 style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 标楷体;\"><u><st