=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Hospitals</strong></span></div><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">MP Shah hospital, Westlands Medical center Avenue health care</span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Shopping and dinning</strong></span></div><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The apartments are minutes away from major malls such as Sarit Centre, Broadwalk mall and Westgate mall.</span></p><div data-w-e-type=\"todo\" style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><input type=\"checkbox\" disabled=\"\" checked=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Excellent road access</strong></span></div><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A short drive to the Nairobi express way allowing easy connectivity to the CBD</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Features and amenities:</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">6-7 Units per floor</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">24 floors dedicated to residential living within a 28 floor development</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">♦Rooftop Gardens </span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">♦Rooftop Swimming Pool</span></p><p style=\"text-align: start; line-height: 1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">♦ Fully Equipped G