ving Area: </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Lounge and dining area</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Open Plan Kitchen: </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Fully fitted with cooker, oven, and hood</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Security: </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Intercom, CCTV surveillance, and 24/7 security</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Other Amenities: </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Elevator in each block, generator, ample parking, and a perimeter wall with an electric fence</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Community: </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Gated community</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> &nbsp;Unit size and price:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> &nbsp;3 Bedroom &nbsp;164 sqm at </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Ksh 18,000,000 (Ksh 17,500,000 for cash buyers)</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> &nbsp; </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Payment Plan:</strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong> &nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A 9-month payment plan is available. </span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><ul><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"></li></ul>',1,'okay',1754292852,1758357485),(240,'TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES','TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES','TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES','TWO RIVERS DUPLEXES',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/de