ther amenities.<br>• Bore hole water supply and adequate water storage system.<br>• On site management office.<br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit sizes and prices:</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">The apartments are sold through three modes of payment, Cash, Mortgage and Tenant Purchase Model.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">• 4 Bedroom – Kshs. 17.1 Million<br>• 3 Bedroom – Kshs. 14.2 Million<br>• 2 Bedroom – Kshs. 11.4 Million</span></p>',1,'',1754295350,1758357229),(242,'THE LOFT RESIDENCIES','THE LOFT RESIDENCIES','THE LOFT RESIDENCIES','THE LOFT RESIDENCIES',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/5db9d32f7181e3ee875f8246ee22e04b5f5c7c8a.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/5db9d32f7181e3ee875f8246ee22e04b5f5c7c8a.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/dd232fbdcdda860135f192553c63ca714eddfa30.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/f5e5cbe89e70cad5a5d4be0cf1d67bdb30676c55.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGK7Gf0dqOQ','https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/dd232fbdcdda860135f192553c63ca714eddfa30.jpg','','36.796680987','-1.212522769',52995,145494,145545,'Kenya / Nairobi / Gigiri','Kenya / Nairobi / Gigiri','1',1780347600,196428.57,55000000.00,55000000.00,'18',28,1,1,0,28,1,280.00,280.00,'<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Loft Residencies</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Modern 4 Bedroom Duplexes with DSQ in Two Rivers Nairobi.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">This project is located in the Diplomatic Blue Zone of Nairobi, Two Rivers.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">making it easy access to key urban nodes such as Westlands, Parklands,<br>Nairobi CBD and Upper hill.</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">This accessibility is assured with 