ortunity to diversify your investment portfolio into Real Estate and earn a minimum return of 20-25% over a 2 year period ( based on standard unit prices and secondary market price point) and thereafter secure recurrent rental income of up to 7.5% yield. The project is located next to Stardom Hotel in Kasarani. Kasarani is the second most populated constituency in Nairobi (with approximately 708,000 residents) hence very high demand for rental units. ​265 Elmer One will be a differentiated high quality product compared to the existing stock in the area making it highly competitive in the rental market ; resulting to high and sustainable occupancy in the development. Available for sale are Studios , 1 bedroom, 1 bedroom loft and 2 bedroom apartments.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Features and amenities:</strong></span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">A gated community with perimeter fencing, internet provision, CCTV surveillance, and manned security.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Upgraded internal drainage system, coordinated landscaping for greenery, 24/7 clean, potable water supply, and backup power for all common areas in the development.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Mobility-friendly development with wheelchair access and a combination of lifts and staircases.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Ample parking spaces for residents and visitors.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Rooftop lounge/garden for entertainment, mini soccer pitch and tennis court.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Harmonized interior design for easy living and maximum indoor comfort.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Unique premium house typologies, unparalleled in the affordable housing market segment e.g. executive studio and 1 bed loft apartment.\\</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 226); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Unit size and price:</strong></span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Studio 21 sqm &nbsp;at Ksh 2,500,000</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">1 Bedroom 60 sqm &nbsp;Ksh 4,950,000</span></li><li><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 Bedrooms 76 sqm Ksh 6,600,000</span></li></ol><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>Payment plan:</strong></span></p><h1><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>10% Deposit </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> followed by flexible period to complete the payment</span></h1><h1><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Total Units: </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><strong>265 </strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"> </span></h1><h1></h1>',1,'okay',1754301730,1758198330),(244,'26 MZIZI COURT APARTMENTS','26 MZIZI COURT APARTMENTS','26 MZIZI COURT APARTMENTS','26 MZIZI COURT APARTMENTS',4,'https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/7cd8039bfe4548e39173bb7d156078fd01a28902.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/52a2f8bf29f53fb2fa5d2438776a21b8f4dfffd5.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/344f249ef76a24d5a3d3860080adf05ea55f7f32.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/bfe1e418545989955cd01c421e3211ab90dc72c1.jpg,https://www.afbeke.com//storage/default/20250804/c513102303724fffe2fdb132a19175b722097299.jpg','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JDSi30d1olo','','','36.79