 style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Type E (113 sqm) – From Ksh 13.2M</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Type E (142 sqm) – From Ksh 16.7M</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Type F (139 sqm) – From Ksh 19.46M</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Enjoy excellent connectivity and convenience with top-tier shopping, schools, offices, and hospitals just minutes away:</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">2 minutes to Westgate & Sarit Centre</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">5 minutes to UN Avenue & Parklands</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Quick access to Gigiri, CBD, and key international schools</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Flexible Payment Plan*</span></p><ul><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">20% deposit to reserve</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Balance spread over 3 years</span></li><li style=\"text-align: start;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">Ideal for off-plan buyers looking for structured, affordable terms</span></li></ul><p style=\"text-align: start;\"><br></p>',1,NULL,1761052966,1761052966);
